description: This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on the east side of South Boston, offering the perfect blend of modern upgrades and outdoor living. Featuring a spacious open kitchen and convenient in-unit laundry, this home is designed for comfort and functionality. Enjoy the privacy of your own deck and yard, ideal for relaxing or entertaining. With a new roof, new windows, and upcoming new siding, this property is move-in ready and poised for long-term durability. Don't miss the opportunity to own a beautiful home in one of South Boston's most sought-after neighborhoods!
